---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Getting Started with AI - Ali Bahrami">
	<main>
		<article class="blog-post">
			<h1>Getting Started with AI</h1>
			<div class="metadata">
				<time datetime="2024-04-20">April 20, 2024</time>
				<span class="category">Artificial Intelligence</span>
			</div>
			
			<div class="content">
				<p>
					Artificial Intelligence has become an integral part of modern technology.
					In this post, we'll explore the fundamental concepts that every beginner
					should know when starting their AI journey.
				</p>
				
				<h2>Key Areas in AI</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Machine Learning</li>
					<li>Deep Learning</li>
					<li>Natural Language Processing</li>
					<li>Computer Vision</li>
				</ul>

				<p>
					We'll dive deeper into each of these topics in future posts. Stay tuned!
				</p>
			</div>
		</article>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 800px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	.blog-post {
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.2;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.metadata {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		font-size: 1rem;
	}
	.metadata time {
		margin-right: 1rem;
	}
	.category {
		padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
		background: rgba(var(--accent-light), 0.1);
		border-radius: 4px;
	}
	.content {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
	}
	h2 {
		font-size: 1.8rem;
		color: rgb(var(--accent-light));
		margin: 2rem 0 1rem;
	}
	ul {
		margin-left: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
</style>